# GenX 360 CRM — AI Microservice Technical Documentation

## Executive Overview

The **GenX 360 AI Microservice** is a specialized FastAPI backend designed to integrate with the GenX 360 Clinic CRM. It provides two core intelligent capabilities:

1. **Module 1 — Image-Based Analysis & Treatment Recommendation**: Analyzes consultation photos (skin, scalp, hair) using a local ONNX computer vision model, maps detected visual indicators to branch specific clinic treatments, and uses GenAI (Google Gemini) to synthesize an objective brief for human consultants.
2. **Module 2 — AI-Driven Upsell Recommendations**: Analyzes client history (package consumption, visit recency, past purchases), scores clients for follow-up readiness using deterministic rules, and generates personalized outreach message drafts using GenAI.

All operations are authenticated via API keys, recorded in a local SQLite/PostgreSQL database for tracking outcomes, and configurable via environment variables.

