        GeminiVis -->|Fallback if down| DetVis["Deterministic Keyword Matcher"]
        Mod1 --> GenBrief["Gemini Text API (Consultant Brief)"]
        Mod2 --> GenUpsell["Gemini Text API (Outreach Generation)"]
