## Core Execution Pipelines

### Pipeline 1: Module 1 — Consultation Image Analysis & Routing

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant UI as Consultation Screen / API
    participant SVC as Service Layer (services.py)
    participant ONNX as ONNX Model Provider
    participant GEM as Gemini API Provider
    participant RULE as Rules Engine (rules.py)
    participant DB as SQLite / Postgres DB

    UI->>SVC: POST /analyze {image_url, image_type, branch_id}
    SVC->>ONNX: Run Local Model Inference (224x224 RGB)
    alt ONNX Success (Confidence >= 0.65)
        ONNX-->>SVC: Return Detected Flags (e.g. ['pigmentation'])
    else ONNX Failure / Low Confidence
        SVC->>GEM: Fallback to Gemini Vision API / Deterministic Matcher
        GEM-->>SVC: Return Detected Flags
    end

    SVC->>RULE: Map Flags to Branch Treatment Catalog
    RULE-->>SVC: Return Ranked Treatment Shortlist

    SVC->>GEM: Generate Consultant Brief (Prompt with Safety Guardrails)
    GEM-->>SVC: Return Consultant Brief Text

    SVC->>DB: Save Analysis Log (analysis_logs)
    SVC-->>UI: Return AnalyzeResponse JSON
```

### Pipeline 2: Module 2 — AI-Driven Client Upsell Recommendations

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant SCHED as Daily Scheduler / Staff Action
    participant SVC as Service Layer (services.py)
    participant CRM as CRM Client (crm_client.py)
    participant RULE as Rules Engine (rules.py)
    participant GEM as Gemini API Provider
    participant DB as Database Storage

    SCHED->>SVC: POST /recommendations/run {branch_id}
    SVC->>CRM: Get Client Historical Data for Branch
    CRM-->>SVC: Return Client List

    loop For Each Client
        SVC->>RULE: Calculate Score & Signals (score_upsell_client)
        RULE-->>SVC: {score, signals, suggested_offer}
        alt Score >= Threshold (60)
            SVC->>GEM: Generate Personal Reason & Outreach Draft
            GEM-->>SVC: {reason, draft_message}
            SVC->>SVC: Append to Recommendation List
        end
    end

    SVC->>DB: Log Recommendations (recommendation_logs)
    SVC->>CRM: Push Recommendations to CRM Server
    SVC-->>SCHED: Return RecommendationRunResponse JSON
```

