## Training & Model Export Pipeline

The project includes an isolated training suite located in `training/` for fine-tuning vision classifiers.

```mermaid
graph LR
    Dataset["Raw Dataset CSV (data/labels.csv)"] --> DataScript["Dataset Splitting (training/dataset.py)"]
    DataScript --> Splits["Train / Val / Test Splits (data/splits/)"]
    Splits --> TrainScript["EfficientNet-B0 Fine-Tuning (training/train.py)"]
    TrainScript --> Checkpoint["PyTorch Checkpoint (checkpoints/best.pth)"]
    Checkpoint --> EvalScript["Model Evaluation (training/evaluate.py)"]
    Checkpoint --> ExportScript["ONNX Exporter (training/export_onnx.py)"]
    ExportScript --> ActiveModel["Active ONNX Model (models/current/model.onnx)"]
```

### Steps to Fine-Tune & Deploy
1. **Install Training Dependencies**:
   `pip install -r training/requirements.txt`
2. **Prepare Dataset & Generate Splits**:
   `python training/dataset.py --csv data/labels.csv --images data/images/ --out data/splits/`
3. **Run Training**:
   `python training/train.py --splits data/splits/ --epochs 20 --out checkpoints/`
4. **Evaluate Model Performance**:
   `python training/evaluate.py --splits data/splits/ --checkpoint checkpoints/best.pth`
5. **Export to ONNX**:
   `python training/export_onnx.py --checkpoint checkpoints/best.pth --out models/current/`

